      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in pristine, showroom condition. Every aspect, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously preserved interior, reflects a history of fastidious ownership. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who demands perfection without compromise.",
