    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve taken such good care of her, and honestly, she looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a scratch or a smudge in sight\u2014it\u2019s truly in pristine, mint condition. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and pampered, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
