    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This is, without exaggeration, the finest example of this model currently on the market. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or door dings, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no wear, the original floor mats are spotless, and all electronics function with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been serviced exclusively at the dealership with a comprehensive folder of records included. Every button, sensor, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 44800.0,
